      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so im working on this new streetwear line and i really dont want it to feel like cultural appropriation or just some cheap imitation. can u help me define what the \"authentic\" urban aesthetic actually looks like these days? like what are the key visual elements or vibes that make something feel truly part of that culture? i want to make sure i'm getting the essence right.",
